These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, 7up, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: american, malaysian, spanish, italian
1. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
2. the italian is on the left or right of the american##3
3. the american is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
5. the american is the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking 7up is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola  | fanta | milk  | 7up |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian      | american | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, colombian, dutch
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, mouse, snake
1. the canadian is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the snake##2
2. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the dutch##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | dutch | colombian | canadian   | brazilian |
| Pet           | mouse      | frog    | turtle | snake      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, pumpkin, banana, nectarine
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, subway, helicopter
1. the person eating pumpkin is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
5. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
6. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | pumpkin | onion | banana     | nectarine |
| Transport   | bike  | helicopter   | subway | motorbike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, cooking, baking, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, martial-arts, horror
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | baking | dancing | cooking | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | martial-arts     | time-travel    | satire       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, peas, apricot, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, fantasy, musical
1. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
3. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
6. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | watermelon   | plum   | peas    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical | crime | fantasy |

