.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, manager, writer, fisherman
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, polish, nigerian, indian
1. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. the coach is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
3. the indian is between the fisherman and the nigerian##2
4. the writer is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | coach | manager | fisherman | writer |
| Nationality   | nigerian        | indian     | colombian       | polish   |

