.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, folk, trance, gospel
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, bird, mouse
1. the owner of the ferret is the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of techno is between the fan of folk and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
5. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
6. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | techno  | trance  | gospel   |
| Pet           | mouse  | hedgehog | bird | ferret |

