.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, kiwi, grapes, avocado
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, nurse, dancer, security-guard
1. the nurse is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
3. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
5. the dancer is somewhere to the left of the chef##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | kiwi     | avocado | grapes     | lime   |
| Job    | security-guard | nurse  | dancer | chef |

