.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, juice, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, pomegranate, carrot, strawberry
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
5. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
6. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | juice | lemonade   | tea |
| Food       | cauliflower       | carrot   | strawberry | pomegranate |

