.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, water, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball, skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
4. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta | water       | milk   | 7up        |
| Sport      | volleyball  | snowboarding | baseball | skateboarding |

