.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks, woodworking, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, cricket, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
5. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | photography | magic-tricks   | woodworking | camping     |
| Sport   | handball     | cycling | cricket  | tennis |

