.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, fantasy, crime, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, volleyball, weightlifting, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | crime        | time-travel        | fantasy |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | parkour | snowboarding | volleyball |

