.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, writing, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, nurse, scientist, police-officer
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
2. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
5. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
6. the scientist is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | woodworking | writing  | skydiving      | drawing |
| Job     | scientist    | police-officer | nurse | architect   |

