.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, water, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, country, metal, d&b
1. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
6. the person drinking water is between the person drinking milk and the fan of country##2
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk   | water  | coffee      | 7up       |
| Music-Genre   | metal | d&b | country | jazz |

