.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, goat, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, tram, boat
1. the owner of the ferret is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the fish##2
2. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | goat   | turtle   | ferret       | fish   |
| Transport   | tram | bus | bike | boat |

