.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, grapefruit, apricot, potato
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, tram, scooter, subway
1. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
5. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
6. the person eating papaya is between the person eating potato and the person driving the bus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapefruit     | potato | papaya | apricot |
| Transport   | scooter | subway | tram      | bus        |

 